Description.Text: A very good quality hotel with friendly service. Metro station in right next to the hotel 11/09 MW
This brand new hotel is centrally located with good transport links to the rest of the city.
Rooms are medium sized, tastefully furnsished and in an excellent condition.
A traditional building with it's own private parking area.
The main restaurant, located on the second floor, is open for breakfast in the monrning. For lunch and dinner Russian and European specialities are served from the a la carte menu
The lobby is large and modern.
